msgid "Help"
msgstr "Msaada"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli inajumuisha maagizo yaliyojengwa ndani ya programu ili kukusaidia "
"kusanidi na kudhibiti usanidi wako."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Ukurasa huu unatoa muhtasari wa vipengele muhimu na viungo vya moja kwa moja"
" mahali ambapo vinaweza kudhibitiwa."

